      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/fertilizer-maker-mosaic-slumps-as-florida-hurricanes-dent-profit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肥料生产商 Mosaic Co. 受美国多起飓风和销售价格下跌影响，利润和销售额大幅低于预期，股价出现一年多来最大跌幅。]]></description>
